[
    {
        "text": "Many people take their right to privacy for granted.",
        "startTime": 3949,
        "endTime": 6885,
        "slowStartTime": 6073,
        "slowEndTime": 10553
    },
    {
        "text": "But most don't realize that this right doesn't extend to the...",
        "startTime": 7430,
        "endTime": 10323,
        "slowStartTime": 11295,
        "slowEndTime": 15710
    },
    {
        "text": "... place where they spend most of their waking hours: their workplace.",
        "startTime": 10452,
        "endTime": 14335,
        "slowStartTime": 15828,
        "slowEndTime": 21727
    },
    {
        "text": "Privacy is one of the most violated principles.",
        "startTime": 15070,
        "endTime": 17964,
        "slowStartTime": 22755,
        "slowEndTime": 27171
    },
    {
        "text": "People do realize monitoring goes on,...",
        "startTime": 18629,
        "endTime": 21035,
        "slowStartTime": 28094,
        "slowEndTime": 31777
    },
    {
        "text": "...but most individuals are unaware of how pervasive the lack of privacy is.",
        "startTime": 21457,
        "endTime": 26278,
        "slowStartTime": 32336,
        "slowEndTime": 39642
    },
    {
        "text": "Monitoring employees electronically and in other ways is a growing part of the way companies do business.",
        "startTime": 27067,
        "endTime": 33507,
        "slowStartTime": 40750,
        "slowEndTime": 50486
    },
    {
        "text": "Some 76% of employers monitor workers' Web connections,...",
        "startTime": 34157,
        "endTime": 38504,
        "slowStartTime": 51385,
        "slowEndTime": 57981
    },
    {
        "text": "... while 50% store and monitor employees' computer files.",
        "startTime": 38976,
        "endTime": 43019,
        "slowStartTime": 58614,
        "slowEndTime": 64754
    },
    {
        "text": "Employers monitor for three main reasons: legal liability issues,...",
        "startTime": 43415,
        "endTime": 47982,
        "slowStartTime": 65272,
        "slowEndTime": 72198
    },
    {
        "text": "...employee productivity, and security breaches.",
        "startTime": 48246,
        "endTime": 50999,
        "slowStartTime": 72519,
        "slowEndTime": 76724
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, e-mail creates a written business record,...",
        "startTime": 51442,
        "endTime": 54907,
        "slowStartTime": 77313,
        "slowEndTime": 82585
    },
    {
        "text": "...and employers are becoming increasingly aware that...",
        "startTime": 55215,
        "endTime": 57779,
        "slowStartTime": 82973,
        "slowEndTime": 86894
    },
    {
        "text": "... e-mail and Internet activity is the electronic equivalent of DNA evidence.",
        "startTime": 57892,
        "endTime": 62780,
        "slowStartTime": 86988,
        "slowEndTime": 94395
    },
    {
        "text": "More than half of all employers block unauthorized phone numbers,...",
        "startTime": 63655,
        "endTime": 67389,
        "slowStartTime": 95633,
        "slowEndTime": 101309
    },
    {
        "text": "...and monitor the amount of time spent on the phone and the numbers dialed.",
        "startTime": 67709,
        "endTime": 71709,
        "slowStartTime": 101713,
        "slowEndTime": 107788
    },
    {
        "text": "More than 80% of the employers who monitor these activities...",
        "startTime": 72419,
        "endTime": 76109,
        "slowStartTime": 108779,
        "slowEndTime": 114388
    },
    {
        "text": "...notify employees about what they are doing.",
        "startTime": 76345,
        "endTime": 78877,
        "slowStartTime": 114667,
        "slowEndTime": 118540
    },
    {
        "text": "Employers use video surveillance in an effort to prevent theft,...",
        "startTime": 79687,
        "endTime": 83394,
        "slowStartTime": 119680,
        "slowEndTime": 125316
    },
    {
        "text": "...violence and sabotage.",
        "startTime": 83516,
        "endTime": 85065,
        "slowStartTime": 125424,
        "slowEndTime": 127822
    },
    {
        "text": "Again more than half of all employers use video monitoring.",
        "startTime": 85593,
        "endTime": 89508,
        "slowStartTime": 128539,
        "slowEndTime": 134487
    },
    {
        "text": "Of those, 85% notify workers of the practice.",
        "startTime": 89941,
        "endTime": 93841,
        "slowStartTime": 135061,
        "slowEndTime": 140986
    },
    {
        "text": "However, video surveillance cameras may be installed in many areas of the workplace,...",
        "startTime": 94299,
        "endTime": 99367,
        "slowStartTime": 141599,
        "slowEndTime": 149276
    },
    {
        "text": "...including locker rooms, leading to a lack of privacy.",
        "startTime": 99779,
        "endTime": 103169,
        "slowStartTime": 149819,
        "slowEndTime": 154978
    },
    {
        "text": "We may not live in Orwell's 1984, but big brother is watching.",
        "startTime": 103776,
        "endTime": 108559,
        "slowStartTime": 155814,
        "slowEndTime": 163064
    }
]